1. Kada *postanu* velike, deca se osamostale. (When they *become* big, children become independent.)
2. Nadam se da ću jednog dana *postati* uspešan biznismen. (I hope that one day I will *become* a successful businessman.)
3. Ukoliko ne budemo brzo reagovali, ova situacija će *postati* još gora. (If we don't react quickly, this situation will *become* even worse.)
4. Neki ljudi žele da *postanu* poznati, ali ne žele da rade za to. (Some people want to *become* famous, but they don't want to work for it.)
5. Kada ljudi *postanu* stariji, često postaju mudriji. (When people *become* older, they often become wiser.)
6. Ne želim da *postanem* kao oni ljudi koji su uvek nezadovoljni. (I don't want to *become* like those people who are always dissatisfied.)
7. Kada seme *postane* biljka, potrebno je više pažnje kako bi rasla. (When the seed *becomes* a plant, it requires more attention to grow.)
8. Nažalost, neke stvari u životu *postanu* teže pre nego što postanu lakše. (Unfortunately, some things in life *become* harder before they become easier.)